<body>
    <div class="fullscreen-image" id="fullscreenImage">
        <div class="image-container">
            <img id="image1" src="https://i.imgur.com/B5qAdLk.jpg" alt="Image 1" class="active">
            <img id="image2" src="https://i.imgur.com/4pTWYr0.jpg" alt="Image 2">
        </div>
        <div class="button-container">
            <button onclick="showImage('image1')">顯示圖片 1</button>
            <button onclick="showImage('image2')">顯示圖片 2</button>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content-section">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="image-side"></div>
            <div class="text-side">
                <h2>標題</h2>
                <p>這是文字說明的範例。可以根據需要添加更多的文字內容。</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="text-side2">
                <h2>標題</h2>
